            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中通服去年純利微升0.09% 擬派末期息0.2241元人幣按年增2.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國通信服務(00552)公布，於2025年度歸屬於公司股東利潤36.1億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年微升0.09%；擬派末期息0.2241元，按年增2.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國通信服務官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240827_FI_source-web_00552.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國通信服務官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240827_FI_source-web_00552.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國通信服務官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司表示，正把握AI時代智算需求爆發等多方面帶來的機遇，積極應對客戶謹慎投資、市場競爭加劇帶來的挑戰，實現經營業績穩中有進，質量效益整體向好。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">去年該公司經營收入達1500.93億元，按年升0.1%。毛利率11.3%，按年減少0.4個百分點，但淨利潤率2.4%，在近4年保持基本穩定。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中通服又表示，將進一步推動「新一代綜合智慧服務商」戰略定位內涵升級，深入實施「人工智能+」行動，將AI紅利轉化為發展新動能。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15817358-%e4%b8%ad%e9%80%9a%e6%9c%8d%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%870-09-%e6%93%ac%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af0-2241%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e2-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/00552-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 12:59:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "AEON信貸全年純利增長16.9% 末期息增至每股0.33元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AEON信貸(00900)公布，截至今年2月底止年度，公司擁有人應佔溢利4.68億元，按年升16.9%；擬派末期息增至每股0.33元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：AEON信貸官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00900-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：AEON信貸官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00900-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：AEON信貸官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入已派中期息0.25元，全年度每股共派0.58元，派付股息比率達51.9%；全年每股派息也較對上年度的0.49元提升18.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內公司收入18.25億元，按年升3.8%。淨利息收入14.17億元，按年增5.2%。減值虧損及減值準備降至4.22億元，按年減5.5%，佔收入比率亦降至23.1%，按年降2.3個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15817271-aeon%e4%bf%a1%e8%b2%b8%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b716-9-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e%e8%87%b3%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a10-33%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00900-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 12:53:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
